{"tid":700302,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[ダブルリーチ]召喚日本麻雀同好","createTime":"2018-06-13T08:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T01:13:09.000Z","uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5dc5b710a5251fccda3cbdf101ba8c2d65d2a2","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEGxq1f0ROAakUWt4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEGxq1f0ROAakUWt4w&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ca53fe00\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEGxq1f0ROAakUWt4w</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎玩厭港式麻雀嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皆んな、マージャングループへようこそ。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d4d6f52933d1e9c43d4064ca5f0b3842cd7277","tid":700302,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"留個靚名交流吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a97cd7f05c97acf979ca44b4a05bf4bbdb500e5","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"日本麻雀玩法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/日本麻雀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%BA%BB%E9%9B%80&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1b872bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/日本麻雀</a><br />\n<br />\n最常見嘅日本麻雀網上對戰系統：天鳳<br />\n<a href=\"http://tenhou.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftenhou.net&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=4567cfae\" target=\"_blank\">http://tenhou.net</a>"},{"pid":"cebb526a536b55df05c7ab1c268c3d36a5ff4b10","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"簡單講 日本麻雀一番起糊（ドラ唔算係坐底嘅一番）<br />\n最後牌山會剩十四隻唔會喺呢局摸到嘅牌<br />\n牌路冇香港牌咁窄 <br />\n未必需要扣牌扣到完場<br />\n而且食糊個規矩係有振聽規則<br />\n所以打一隻牌都需要比香港牌更謹慎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3c6e0be3b603bee1d775530b6d3a15850509d6","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b7ddabb1870708314e387ed95c15c938939146","tid":700302,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"有打過下麻格雀龍門同天鳳<br />\n不過好耐冇打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5f18bfd880b6d753ceb394fa626dc3ef422238","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9b7ddabb1870708314e387ed95c15c938939146","tid":700302,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"有打過下麻格雀龍門同天鳳<br />\n不過好耐冇打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"入嚟約戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b1d7bd69a41078e0ab73870a5df5583d83d83c","tid":700302,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73df915b74f194c6e213740eda02f874646fa160","tid":700302,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cfb0e5cfc5d5773f0be77beeb6aa5da53fbe34","tid":700302,"uid":157224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"打開廣東牌,歡唔歡迎新手?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"